NAME: ACCOUNTADMIN
COMMENT: Account administrator can manage all aspects of the account.

NAME: PUBLIC
COMMENT: Public role is automatically available to every user in the account.

NAME: ORGADMIN
COMMENT: Organization administrator can manage organizations and accounts in organizations

NAME: SECURITYADMIN
COMMENT: Security administrator can manage security aspects of the account.

NAME: SYSADMIN
COMMENT: System administrator can create and manage databases and warehouses.
